      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/hscb-executives-tell-hk-shareholders-focus-on-dividends-remains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司的高级管理人员在香港举行的投资者会议上向股东保证，该银行仍专注于支付股息。]]></description>
